Privacy Policy

Last updated: October 17, 2024.

Welcome to Globe Defender!

This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use my mobile application Globe Defender (the "App").

1. Information We Collect
Personally Identifiable Information (PII):

We do not collect any personally identifiable information directly through my App.

Non-Personally Identifiable Information:

Usage data such as gameplay statistics, session length, and in-game actions.
While we do not collect personally identifiable information directly, the Appodeal SDK and certain ad networks may collect non-personally identifiable information. This can include:
Technical device data (e.g., device model, user-agent)
Other device data (e.g., device type, current device state, screen brightness, etc.)
Network information (e.g., provider, connection type)
Other identifiers (e.g., IP address, MCC-MNC)
Please note that third-party services like the Appodeal SDK may have their own privacy practices, and we encourage users to review their policies for more information.

2. Data Transmission
The App may transmit non-personally identifiable information such as usage data to our servers or to third-party analytics providers to improve the game experience and for analytics purposes.

3. How We Use Your Data
To improve game functionality and user experience.
To analyze usage patterns to enhance our services.
To fix bugs and ensure the security of the App.

4. Data Deletion Requests
You can request the deletion of your data by contacting us at huibergs.games@gmail.com. We will respond to your request within a reasonable timeframe.

5. App Permissions
The App requires access to the following:
Google Play Profile Name: This permission is needed to save your results to leaderboards. This is strictly for leaderboard functionality and is not stored outside of this use.
The App does not require access to location data.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, or if you need to report a security vulnerability, please contact us at: huibergs.games@gmail.com

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update the Privacy Policy from time to time and will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

